          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>soy sauce</strong>, <strong>sriracha </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>ginger & garlic paste</strong> to a bowl with 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml]</span> <strong>water</strong> and your <strong>cornflour </strong>and mix until smooth – this is your <strong>spicy stir-fry sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1627380512004-x200.jpg",
